Feline2::

She stood back. "You want to reprogram me?" Her Allience program and 
her fear were working against her."No. I don't want to be 
reprogramed. I knew it. You want to turn me in so they can kill me."

She ran out of the lab and out the entrance of the base. She 
transformed into leopard and ran at full speed away from the base.
